data.enText: a university or college student who is studying for their first degree

data.chText: 大学本科课程 / 学生 / 学位

tr: a university student who has not yet received a first degree

value.def: An undergraduate is a student at a university or college who is studying for his or her first degree.

example.ex: Economics undergraduates are probably the brightest in the university.
example.tran: 经济学专业的本科生可能是大学里最聪明的学生。
